WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.890 --> 00:00:05.160
Homemade omelet - a perfect dish for a hearty breakfast.

00:00:05.160 --> 00:00:08.319
The main thing in this omelet is its puffy and airy.

00:00:08.319 --> 00:00:13.879
Today, I will cook an unusual omelet, which I found recently.

00:00:13.879 --> 00:00:16.329
For this recipe, we need:

00:00:16.329 --> 00:00:20.900
4 eggs, 2 tbsp of milk, 50 g of cheese, pepper and salt to taste.

00:00:20.900 --> 00:00:24.710
A little vegetable oil.

00:00:24.710 --> 00:00:28.230
Put the frying pan to warm up.

00:00:28.230 --> 00:00:30.380
A small fire.

00:00:30.380 --> 00:00:34.110
While the frying pan is heating up, we are quickly preparing our ingredients.

00:00:34.110 --> 00:00:43.870
Separate the egg whites from the egg yolks.

00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:53.320
Add a little salt in egg yolks.

00:00:53.330 --> 00:01:01.860
A little bit of ground pepper, to taste.

00:01:01.860 --> 00:01:05.080
Pour milk.

00:01:05.080 --> 00:01:09.980
Beat until smooth and lemon colored.

00:01:10.930 --> 00:01:13.550
Add a little salt in egg whites.

00:01:13.550 --> 00:01:16.090
It is necessary to add salt.

00:01:16.090 --> 00:01:24.010
Beat egg whites with electric mixer on high speed until stiff but not dry.

00:01:27.270 --> 00:01:28.509
Egg whites are ready.

00:01:28.509 --> 00:01:31.230
They are so thick.

00:01:31.230 --> 00:01:34.290
Check the heating of frying pan.

00:01:34.290 --> 00:01:37.960
Drip with water on the surface of the frying pan.

00:01:37.960 --> 00:01:40.880
Water drops are running.

00:01:40.880 --> 00:01:48.730
The surface is well heated.

00:01:48.730 --> 00:01:54.650
Take a little bit of vegetable oil.

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:09.380
Pour egg yolk here.

00:02:12.679 --> 00:02:18.459
As a pancake.

00:02:18.459 --> 00:02:21.060
Cook.

00:02:21.060 --> 00:02:23.219
It is literally about 1 minute.

00:02:23.219 --> 00:02:30.939
It begins to fry.

00:02:36.639 --> 00:02:40.059
Let's wait a little more.

00:02:40.059 --> 00:02:43.279
On the one side it is already fried.

00:02:43.279 --> 00:02:51.359
Place egg whites on top.

00:02:53.519 --> 00:02:55.499
It is beautiful.

00:02:55.499 --> 00:02:58.269
Spread on top.

00:02:58.269 --> 00:03:06.229
Gently level surface.

00:03:13.919 --> 00:03:17.519
Cook on low heat.

00:03:17.519 --> 00:03:21.100
Cook until puffy and bottom is light brown.

00:03:21.100 --> 00:03:26.599
Now it can be easily pierced with spatula, sticks to the fingers.

00:03:26.599 --> 00:03:30.599
Cook until knife inserted in center comes out clean.

00:03:31.559 --> 00:03:36.189
Do not cover with a lid.

00:03:36.189 --> 00:03:40.120
While cooking an omelet, take a fine grater.

00:03:40.120 --> 00:03:44.820
Grate the cheese.

00:03:45.889 --> 00:03:48.039
It took about 3 minutes.

00:03:48.039 --> 00:03:51.779
Check the edges. Carefully lift omelet at edge to see color.

00:03:51.779 --> 00:03:55.819
Egg whites became elastic.

00:03:55.820 --> 00:04:03.819
Sprinkle with cheese.

00:04:03.819 --> 00:04:09.419
A little bit.

00:04:09.419 --> 00:04:12.449
Turn off the heat.

00:04:12.449 --> 00:04:21.400
Cut the omelet into 2 parts.

00:04:31.449 --> 00:04:39.609
Fold omelet in half, being careful not to break it. Slip onto warm serving plate.

00:04:44.419 --> 00:04:48.300
This airy omelet is a perfect breakfast for the whole family! Serve with salsa or tomato pasta sauce.

00:04:48.340 --> 00:04:51.880
Cook with pleasure and enjoy!

